.TH FSATFETCH 1 "June 29, 2026"
.SH NAME
fsatfetch \- cure your bad habit of mistyping
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B fsatfetch
[
.B \-alFc
]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B fsatfetch
is a highly advanced animation program for curing your bad habit of mistyping.
.PP
.TP
.B \-a
An accident is occurring. People cry for help.
.TP
.B \-l
Little version.
.TP
.B \-F
It flies like the galaxy express 999.
.TP
.B \-c
C51 appears instead of D51.
.SH BUGS
It sometimes lists system specs.
